\f2\b\fs28 \cf0 \strokec2 1. Mudarabah & Musharakah Pricing \'97 The $3 Trillion Gap\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0\fs24 \cf0 This is perhaps the most important one. Mudarabah (silent partnership) and Musharakah (joint venture) are the two foundational halal financing structures. They are supposed to be the Islamic alternative to loans. The problem is that 
\f2\b no mathematical pricing model for mudarabah exists
\f0\b0 . Islamic banks just use rough heuristics \'97 they target a "profit rate" that ends up matching LIBOR/SOFR anyway, making it interest in everything but name.\
The Ackerer random time representation solves this completely. A mudarabah contract works as follows: the rabb-al-mal (capital provider) invests; the mudarib (manager) runs the project; at project completion \'97 a random time \uc0\u952  \'97 profits are split according to the agreed ratio. The fair price of the capital provider's stake today is exactly:\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f3\fs26 \cf0 f_t = E^Q_t [ profit_share \'d7 x_\uc0\u952  ]\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f0\fs24 \cf0 where x_\uc0\u952  is the project value at the random completion time \u952 , and \u952  has an exponential distribution with intensity \u954  \'97 the project completion hazard rate. This is Theorem 3 directly. The \u954  is estimable from historical project completion data in any industry.\
For Musharakah (ongoing joint venture), the continuous premium \uc0\u954  \'d7 (current_value - contributed_capital) \'d7 dt is paid between partners as the project evolves \'97 exactly the funding payment structure. No interest. The math proves it's no-arbitrage.\
What this means practically: 
\f2\b every Islamic bank in the world could replace its LIBOR-linked profit rates with a mathematically rigorous, interest-free pricing model
\f0\b0 . The $3 trillion Islamic finance industry has been waiting for this for 50 years without knowing the tool existed.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \strokec3 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa280\partightenfactor0

\f2\b\fs28 \cf0 \strokec2 2. Ijara (Islamic Lease) and Diminishing Musharakah \'97 Islamic Mortgages\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0\fs24 \cf0 Ijara is Islamic lease \'97 the basis of Islamic mortgages, auto finance, and equipment finance globally. Currently the rental payment schedule is set by discounting future rentals at an interest rate equivalent \'97 riba is embedded in the pricing even though the cashflows look different.\
With Ackerer: model rental income as a continuous flow at rate \uc0\u954  \'d7 asset_value \'d7 dt. The lease termination is the stopping time \u952 . The fair capital value of the leased asset today is:\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f3\fs26 \cf0 f_t = E^Q_t [ asset_value_at_\uc0\u952  ] = \u954 /(\u954  + depreciation_rate) \'d7 current_value\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f0\fs24 \cf0 No interest rate benchmark needed. \uc0\u954  is calibrated from rental yield data and asset depreciation.\
Diminishing Musharakah \'97 how Islamic home finance works, where the bank and buyer gradually share ownership until the buyer owns 100% \'97 can be modeled as a sequence of stopping times \uc0\u952 \u8321 , \u952 \u8322 , ... Each tranche buyout is priced by the formula. The entire amortization schedule that currently mirrors a mortgage becomes derivable from \u954  alone.\
This restructures the entire Islamic mortgage industry, which has been unable to escape SOFR/LIBOR linkage since inception.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \strokec3 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa280\partightenfactor0

