\f0\b0\fs24 \cf0 In Islamic finance, paying royalties on intellectual property \'97 software licences, music, patents \'97 raises questions about the nature of the asset. But as a pricing problem, royalty streams are straightforwardly handled by Theorem 6: a royalty contract pays \uc0\u966 (x_\u952 ) at random usage events \u952 , where x_\u952  is the market price of the IP at the usage event.\
